terrorist - the objective is to choose the weapon down the ramp and try to penetrate the stronghold of the ct's. 
counter-terrorism - the objective is to choose the weapon and defend the fortress. 

Extra: The terrorists can catch awp's on top of the fortress 

weapons: 

CV47 - AMMO 120 
M4A1 - 120 AMMO 
AWP - AMMO 0; ONLY 10 BULLETS
